snippet.title: 4TheMarauders
snippet.description:
Name: 4TheMarauders
Age: 22
Gender: Male
Birthplace: Los Angeles, CA

-I create fan made trailers of upcoming DC/Marvel movies and I create an original story with DC and Marvel characters.
-Editing since 2012
-I also edit, write, and direct short films
-Favorite comic book character is Batman
-I usually post videos either on Wednesday, Friday, or Sunday
-Winner of the YEA Award for Most Improved Editor (2016), Best Original Story (2017), and Best Trailer Series (2017)
-Current Series is DC Marvel:The Dark Apocalypse Strikes Back
-I accept requests but not guaranteed to make all of them
-Favorite Comic-book Film: The Dark Knight
